---
---
<section class="bg-white dark:bg-[#0b0f19] layout bound-x py-[32px] m-0 border-0 transition-colors duration-300 scheme-default relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="w-full h-full">
    <div class="max-w-screen-vp10 mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <span class="typo-label text-[var(--scheme-accent)] mb-4 block transition-colors duration-300">An API for complex problems, engineered for developers</span>
      <h2 class="typo-h2 max-w-3xl mx-auto transition-colors duration-300">
        Your shortcut to complex scheduling optimization
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid vp9:grid-cols-2 gap-10 justify-center">
      <div class="bg-[var(--scheme-shade)] p-10 rounded-3xl border border-[var(--scheme-border)] transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="h-12 w-12 text-[var(--scheme-accent)] mb-6 opacity-80 drop-shadow-sm">
           <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="typo-h3 mb-4 transition-colors duration-300">Maximize productivity</h3>
        <p class="typo-p transition-colors duration-300">
          Get the most value continuously out of your vehicles and field service technicians. Plan more jobs in less time while satisfying all complex constraints.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-[var(--scheme-shade)] p-10 rounded-3xl border border-[var(--scheme-border)] transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:shadow-md">
         <div class="h-12 w-12 text-[var(--scheme-accent)] mb-6 opacity-80 drop-shadow-sm">
           <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="typo-h3 mb-4 transition-colors duration-300">Cut travel times & costs</h3>
        <p class="typo-p transition-colors duration-300">
          Create highly efficient and robust schedules that adapt to road networks and real-time transit matrix disruptions seamlessly.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-[var(--scheme-shade)] p-10 rounded-3xl border border-[var(--scheme-border)] transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:shadow-md">
         <div class="h-12 w-12 text-[var(--scheme-accent)] mb-6 opacity-80 drop-shadow-sm">
           <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="typo-h3 mb-4 transition-colors duration-300">Reduce carbon footprint</h3>
        <p class="typo-p transition-colors duration-300">
          Minimize total driven distance and transition successfully to eco-friendly options by balancing mixed fleets perfectly.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-[var(--scheme-shade)] p-10 rounded-3xl border border-[var(--scheme-border)] transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:shadow-md">
         <div class="h-12 w-12 text-[var(--scheme-accent)] mb-6 opacity-80 drop-shadow-sm">
           <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="typo-h3 mb-4 transition-colors duration-300">Uphold customer SLAs</h3>
        <p class="typo-p transition-colors duration-300">
           Guarantee tight time-window commitments to your customers without sacrificing the overall route efficiency and density of schedules.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
